{"tid":2491802,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"2021 倫敦市長選舉直擊 Farah London 定 Shaun Bailey!?","createTime":"2021-04-16T14:41:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T14:49:43.000Z","uid":29979,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"17cfac019fdf706255800ec42a02389f19807378","tid":2491802,"uid":29979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T14:41:36.000Z","msg":"眾所週知 Mayor Of London 2021將會係<br />\n2021年5月6日舉行<br />\n<br />\n我幫大家做左個懶人包<br />\n希望香港人去到英國 都盡番個公民責任<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"purple\">現任市長 Sadiq Khans</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3xaJoXQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3xaJoXQ.png&h=e8995c87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/sadiqkhan?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsadiqkhan%3Fs%3D21&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLf3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=53b6a7ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/sadiqkhan?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n現任市長<br />\n好多貪污醜聞<br />\n無咩幫香港人既消息<br />\n最出名係用左&pound;2,000,000做全球個人PR<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"blue\">保守黨候選人 Shaun Bailey </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qaZJ8p7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqaZJ8p7.png&h=6a024555&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/sadiqkhan?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsadiqkhan%3Fs%3D21&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLf3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=53b6a7ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/sadiqkhan?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n有提話幫香港人<br />\n出過廣東話廣告<br />\n話會幫香港人融入英國<br />\n但twitter social media一面倒反對佢<br />\nMedia 仲話係100年黎最差既候選人<br />\n<br />\n事緣前排有個英國女仔Sarah Everard<br />\n夜晚出街之後，返屋企被尾隨，<br />\n隔一排之後，喺好遠既Lent搵返條屍<br />\n仲發現係被警察所殺害嘅<br />\n<br />\n佢出咗一個政治抽水post，全世界都叫佢delete<br />\n但係佢話冇問題唔肯<br />\n<br />\n其實佢都幾多花邊新聞，但每一個都係negative impact ，media什至笑佢「任何野都可以變成negative既候選人」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最重要係英國人 普遍唔想PM同mayor of London係同一個政黨<br />\n怕所有政策都一棍打落嚟，無得反抗<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"orange\">獨立候選人 Farah London</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xBcGU6H.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxBcGU6H.png&h=7415aacd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/sadiqkhan?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsadiqkhan%3Fs%3D21&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLf3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=53b6a7ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/sadiqkhan?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n十月出post要追究 英藉黑警陶輝<br />\n好似已經入左司法程序<br />\n<br />\n有去香港人集會舉 光復旗<br />\n<br />\n周不時都會發聲<br />\n<br />\n候開社區活動，近幾個月開始紅，仲上埋BBC<br />\n<br />\n但因為英國生態好著重 有無「被投過票」所以一直告急緊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今年有成20個候選人<br />\n其他香港人可能唔識既我就唔一一介紹<br />\n<br />\n但以下呢幾個比較出名既反派<br />\n分別係<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"teal\">Lawrence Fox 英國演員</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eGuFreC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeGuFreC.png&h=21edbb79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢主要係反Lock Down 話上任後 唔洗再戴口罩 同唔會有social restriction <br />\n<br />\n類似既有digital marketing<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"teal\">好強勁既Brain Rose</span></span><br />\n呢個人<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZSM8z8j.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZSM8z8j.png&h=609321d0&s={SIZE}\" />比較奇怪<br />\n<br />\n成日social media post 自己做gym<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CNsYARVHMPZ/?igshid=q6scxaxo2pyc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCNsYARVHMPZ%2F%3Figshid%3Dq6scxaxo2pyc&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLf3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=5470c9b1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCNsYARVHMPZ%2F%3Figshid%3Dq6scxaxo2pyc&h=28a4d361\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CNsYARVHMPZ/?igshid=q6scxaxo2pyc</a><br />\n<br />\n因為都放左幾多budget去宣傳都叫人有識<br />\n<br />\n所有候選人既list 同汁係呢度<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CNsYARVHMPZ/?igshid=q6scxaxo2pyc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCNsYARVHMPZ%2F%3Figshid%3Dq6scxaxo2pyc&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLf3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=5470c9b1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCNsYARVHMPZ%2F%3Figshid%3Dq6scxaxo2pyc&h=28a4d361\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CNsYARVHMPZ/?igshid=q6scxaxo2pyc</a><br />\n<br />\n如果香港人去到英國<br />\n真係應該盡下責任，無論住邊度都好<br />\n記得投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d8c1956461997aec24c676d1dd8b715ce4f9198","tid":2491802,"uid":29979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T14:42:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/medicine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/medicine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/medicine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/medicine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所有候選人list <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-55748037.amp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fuk-england-london-55748037.amp&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLf3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=03cc116d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-55748037.amp</a>"},{"pid":"5a5839a2cec4b545b258f50363d78f43dfcc117a","tid":2491802,"uid":29979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T14:42:56.000Z","msg":"候選人list貼錯左 做 Brain陣起身<br />\n<br />\n補番係pin到<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cross.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29af56eb67946facf0f19462fc9d619ba98f3a2a","tid":2491802,"uid":13644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T14:43:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24e28125966455ce895b1e12036dea23a65369cc","tid":2491802,"uid":29979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T14:44:26.000Z","msg":"登記做選民要係4月19之前去<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/register-to-vote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fregister-to-vote&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLf3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=7d76a27a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/register-to-vote</a><br />\n登記<br />\n<br />\n有地址 同有效visa (bno 都得） 就可以登記<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"639b71ce5512f4440d979107c0a6f3948c05d0cc","tid":2491802,"uid":29979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T14:45:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/miracle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4a3024c3ff12a8ff90e195cb01e75404a4fe9a4","tid":2491802,"uid":29979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T14:45:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/coffin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cross.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73f7e82876bc1fa2be446efeaf3f5d5e5853ff65","tid":2491802,"uid":29979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T14:45:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3396b5ff205ca6c4f9ca20604e3196d7aefa27c7","tid":2491802,"uid":29979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T14:45:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/medicine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1bbe26ad36b66be280d20f96251b7a78053f429","tid":2491802,"uid":29979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T14:46:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/miracle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b304da179c9803b43daf2da913cddf9a29e6b9fb","tid":2491802,"uid":29979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T14:46:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cross.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dd3d145f60031568de54ed72f6e04f64e6a4825","tid":2491802,"uid":29979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T14:47:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c84fe4bd348ad5c4c513c612dd88fd988f8f5807","tid":2491802,"uid":29979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T14:47:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8c0ff61e86154747f75f2c252424b12b0d44742","tid":2491802,"uid":29979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T14:48:13.000Z","msg":"認真post無人理"},{"pid":"f7737475c41b944488789cb11b4720a17fedc92d","tid":2491802,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T14:49:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hair.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ffb527cdf3153aa7fc43777afb890c84aeadecf","tid":2491802,"uid":248540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T14:49:43.000Z","msg":"想問尾果兩個係左定右?"}],"pinned":{"pid":"8d8c1956461997aec24c676d1dd8b715ce4f9198","tid":2491802,"uid":29979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T14:42:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/medicine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/medicine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/medicine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/medicine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所有候選人list <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-55748037.amp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fuk-england-london-55748037.amp&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLf3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=03cc116d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-55748037.amp</a>"}}